# Hard Boiled Eggs

Based on [Kenji](https://www.seriouseats.com/the-secrets-to-peeling-hard-boiled-eggs) and [Ethan](https://newsletter.ethanchlebowski.com/p/peeling-eggs-perfectly-every-time). Previously based on [https://downshiftology.com/recipes/perfect-soft-boiled-hard-boiled-eggs](https://downshiftology.com/recipes/perfect-soft-boiled-hard-boiled-eggs)

